The '''Lord of the Rings movie site''', or [http://www.lordoftherings.net www.lordoftherings.net] is the official site for [[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|''The Lord of the Rings'' (film series)]].  Included on this site are interviews, news, basic weapon/character information, and other media based on the movie trilogy.
